{"tid":2264891,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【女生暴動罪不成立　心繫被送中 12 港人】","createTime":"2020-10-31T04:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T16:31:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2c22993e4bb3950a6c97497da4ed86efc42e08","tid":2264891,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/123246836_3602921596460101_4645317106973685298_n.png?_nc_cat=107&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=qPrsajQl21IAX9t3KxD&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=13b1ec175e74a64ff019f96a9c2696b5&amp;oe=5FC22549\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F123246836_3602921596460101_4645317106973685298_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DqPrsajQl21IAX9t3KxD%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3D13b1ec175e74a64ff019f96a9c2696b5%26oe%3D5FC22549&h=65beb5bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019.8.31 灣仔衝突案 7 人今獲裁定參與暴動等罪名全部不成立，其中一名被告仍心繫於內地遭扣留的 12 名港人，於其隨身袋上扣上「#Save 12 HKYOUTHS」黑色絲帶。她在步出法庭後，也舉起相關標語。<br />\n<br />\n【相關報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HPNseC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HPNseC&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=38034bb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HPNseC</a> 】<br />\n<br />\n「陣地社工」成員陳虹秀等8人，被控去年 8 月 31 日在灣仔參與暴動案，法官沈小民早前裁定陳虹秀的暴動罪表證不成立，當庭獲釋，餘下7名被告則繼續處理，並於今日裁決，法官裁定7人暴動罪不成立，第四被告另被控的一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器亦不成立。<br />\n<br />\n法官宣佈各被告罪名不成立一刻，庭內隨即掌聲雷動。散庭後有被告難掩激動，失聲痛哭，有被告與親友及律師相擁致謝，眾人均眼泛淚光，場面感人，期間有人指「呢個先係正常結果」，亦有人指「好似突然派彩咁」，更有親友向罪名不成立的被告表示，「你聽日可以準時返工啦」，對方回答「係呀，可以返工啦」，如釋重負。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3602921593126768/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3602921593126768%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=f0d00dba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3602921593126768/</a>"},{"pid":"b54cb2ce81ceac22fdb66013093443c7516f58a7","tid":2264891,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T04:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b223b47a2dba27eaa250f8a693aa261b98efbfd2","tid":2264891,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abcd05014a1726ebdf5dd0fd8ba31c5e6dedfba","tid":2264891,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d66ceba947fc2c5531be8f5b248a7ccce30b1da","tid":2264891,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2beca2236d40e20f2dfa5b04a07ac65dd7294850","tid":2264891,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45299a2d0a97b950863697e236613de7b890f022","tid":2264891,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a